<p>In an updated video, after being warned of his crime in the comments section, the teen went on: 'I know what I'm doing, I did this before,' she said. 'My ex was in jail, so I know what I'm doing.' </p>

<p>However, things didn't work out for Gavon and Amaya, and he stopped writing when he realised their messages were being shared on social media.</p>

